{"tid":688512,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"分享一下以前讀書時代既唔同節目活動","createTime":"2018-06-03T09:44:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-03T10:45:51.000Z","uid":102938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2972a8123d880bb05e2e1bf14bf8990e38bd18d9","tid":688512,"uid":102938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T09:44:16.000Z","msg":"讀書時代節目活動：<br />\n<br />\n課室或小食部或籃球場或是旦搵地方（M記）吹水hea<br />\n圖書館做功課或玩電腦或瞓教<br />\n大時大節學校party或特別活動（音樂日）<br />\n私底下班會活動（最興BBQ邊爐大排檔）<br />\n打波踢波閃避球桌球等<br />\n去朋友家打機，同埋玩三國殺等卡game<br />\n網吧打機（當年玩War3，後期玩LOL）同埋玩手機<br />\n睇戲行山釣魚行街（學校附近地方或放假時出旺角深水埗）<br />\n學校搞既camp（學生會社幹事）同埋興趣班（例如棋藝學會捉象棋）<br />\n<br />\n當然仲有最重要，老師為我地而設既開心補課活動啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1ca34506d0326b346d7c4b832394d200e80b56f","tid":688512,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T09:47:05.000Z","msg":"日日屌下閪咁<br />\n畢業後十年都冇屌過閪<br />\n太貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d47652dd0c54f00347ec7aa8750f965881c7ddf4","tid":688512,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T10:29:01.000Z","msg":"返屋企打機"},{"pid":"6dcf59b862691783c985592152cbc00dc69838d6","tid":688512,"uid":139676,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T10:30:09.000Z","msg":"做ptbf"},{"pid":"1b8d52c3fd14bc7f6f2eabc86d166429fed1be07","tid":688512,"uid":128070,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T10:45:51.000Z","msg":"分享下？有無分享上？"}]}